Anna is enjoying the best phase of her life. Yes, she is pregnant and looks very happy these days. One day suddenly she has started feeling pain in her stomach. Without making any delays, call 911 so that the ambulance can reach there on time. There are many things to do before the ambulance arrives and after reaching the hospital. Join Annas Baby Twins Birth and get ready to take care of this cute princess and her twins in your own style!

Make sure that she gets some sweet kisses from her true love (husband), enough water and a sufficient amount of oxygen on time. Upon reaching the hospital, she has given the birth of twins. Wow! It will be your responsibility to provide her and her twins with the needful medical care in this brand new doctor game. Use a soft towel to clean them and make sure that you will also cute their umbilical cords! Weigh them by putting babies in their beds. 

Shower some powder on them and put on fresh diapers on both the cute babies! Give them proper blankets so it will be easy for their mommy to hold them up in this one of the best html5 surgery games for kids! Do not forget to give her a pill for her fastest recovery after the birth of babies! Then send babies to their mother so that she can breast feed them. Hurry up! Kristoff is waiting for his two cute babies outside. Good luck to have a blast in our online princess games for children, no download required!
